summaries.short: Sam discovers the truth about his connection to Osea Island and fights to escape.
summaries.full: Sam is shocked to learn the truth about his connection to Osea and the islanders’ intentions for his future. Later, in a fight for his life, Sam tries desperately to escape their clutches and make it back to the mainland in one piece.

summaries.short: Helen brings her two daughters to Osea, but their trip takes an ominous turn while the family looks for a place to stay.
summaries.full: Winter. Helen surprises her two daughters, Tallulah and Ellie, with a trip to Osea Island for Ellie’s birthday. After finding that the cottage she booked is suspiciously no longer available, Helen scours the island for a place to stay, but finds resistance at every turn.

summaries.short: In his quest to learn more about the islanders, Sam has a series of haunting encounters as Osea prepares for a dry run of the festival.
summaries.full: Plagued by a disturbing dream, Sam awakes to find himself in a compromising situation and, having missed the morning crossing to return to the mainland, spends the day trying to learn more about the islanders. After a series of terrifying events leaves him shaken, Sam plots a way off Osea, but is convinced to stay put as the islanders prepare for a dry run of their big event.

summaries.short: Series premiere. After Londoner Sam rescues a young girl in the woods, he takes her home to the mysterious Osea Island.
summaries.full: Series premiere. After Sam, a London family man in crisis, rescues a young girl in the woods, he brings her home to the ominous Osea Island, where inhabitants are preparing for a curious annual festival. As he meets Osea’s secretive locals, Sam grows increasingly desperate to return to the mainland to make an important call – but the island proves difficult to escape.

summaries.short: Series finale. With a fractious battle for power brewing, Helen and her family find themselves trapped in the middle.
summaries.full: Series finale. With a battle for power brewing, Helen comes face to face with what she’s been searching for since arriving on the island. When the sisters are separated, Tallulah witnesses a gruesome act of violence, and Ellie learns of their mother’s hidden agenda. As tensions reach a fever pitch for all those on Osea Island, Helen and her girls make a final attempt to escape.
